Detailed changes:\n- Gateway contracts: v2 DecryptionRegistry/InputVerificationRegistry updates, GatewayConfig apiUrl exposure, deployment task reads KMS/Coprocessor API URLs, tests/mocks adjusted.\n- Coprocessor: gw-listener API now verifies commitments, returns signed InputVerification + GetCiphertextResponse; new migration for verify_proofs commitment.\n- KMS connector: gw-listener stores anchor block data; KMS API returns anchorBlock + shareIndex; KMS worker fetches coprocessor API and verifies GetCiphertextResponse signatures; new DB migration for decryption request block info.\n- Host contracts: DecryptionFallback signature payload alignment for user decrypt requests.\n- Test-suite: coprocessor signing key mounted, GatewayConfig env includes API URLs + signer address; KMS connector signer address propagated; deploy script sequencing improved for KMS shareIndex.\n- Docs/changelog: v2 plan/test docs and CHANGELOG updated; cold path deferred, hot path focus.
